query:
SELECT
                (
                    ts.id,
                    ts.owner,
                    ts.hostname,
                    ts.port,
                    ts.countries,
                    ts.auth_token_randomizer,
                    ts.base_secret_index,
                    ts.weight,
                    ts.ipv4_score,
                    ts.ipv6_score,
                    ts.srv4_score,
                    ts.srv6_score
                ) AS "time_source!: TimeSource",
                u.email AS "user_email!"
            FROM time_source_scores AS ts
            LEFT JOIN users AS u ON ts.owner = u.id
            WHERE ts.deleted = false;
